# ğŸš€ TOP INTERVIEW Q&A â€” Docker Image & Container

---

### âœ… **Q1: Docker Image kya hota hai?**

**Answer:**
Docker Image ek **template/blueprint** hota hai jisme application chalane ke liye
sab kuch include hota hai:

* OS base (Ubuntu/Alpine)
* Required software (Java, Python, Node)
* Code + Dependencies

ğŸ“Œ Ye read-only hota hai.

ğŸ“Œ Ek image se multiple containers bana sakte hain.

---

### âœ… **Q2: Docker Container kya hota hai?**

**Answer:**
Container ek **running instance** of an image hota hai.

* Lightweight hota hai
* Isolated environment deta hai
* Fast start hota hai (milliseconds)

ğŸ“Œ Container = Application actually run hoti hai yaha

---

### âœ… **Q3: Image aur Container me exact difference?**

| Feature    | Image                         | Container                  |
| ---------- | ----------------------------- | -------------------------- |
| Nature     | Read-Only                     | Run-Time (changes allowed) |
| Purpose    | Blueprint                     | Execution                  |
| Quantity   | 1 Image â†’ Multiple Containers | Each is an instance        |
| Similarity | Recipe                        | Ready Food ğŸ±              |

---

### âœ… **Q4: Container VM (Virtual Machine) se better kyu?**

| Container           | VM                   |
| ------------------- | -------------------- |
| Host OS share karta | Separate OS required |
| MB size             | GB size              |
| Fast boot (sec)     | Slow boot (mins)     |
| Low resource usage  | High resource usage  |
| Portable            | Less portable        |

**Conclusion:** Container â†’ Faster â†’ Lightweight â†’ DevOps friendly âœ…

---

### âœ… **Q5: Dockerfile kya hota hai?**

**Answer (short & smart):**
Dockerfile ek script hota hai jisme hum **image ka recipe** likhte hain.
Docker isko padh ke image banata hai.

---

### âœ… **Q6: Docker Hub kya hai?**

**Answer:**
Images ka **Public Registry** jaha se images pull kar ke use kar sakte:

Example:

```
docker pull nginx
docker pull mysql
```

---

### âœ… **Q7: Docker image kaise banti hai?**

**Answer:**

```
Dockerfile â†’ docker build â†’ Image
```

Command:

```
docker build -t myimage:v1 .
```

---

### âœ… **Q8: Container kaise run hota hai?**

Command:

```
docker run -d -p 8080:80 nginx
```

---

### âœ… **Q9: Container ko stop/start/remove kaise?**

```
docker stop container_id
docker start container_id
docker rm container_id
```

---

### âœ… **Q10: Container delete ho jaye to data safe kaise?**

Volume use karte:

```
docker volume create mydata
```

ğŸ“Œ Volume = Permanent storage

---

### âœ… **Q11: Layered Architecture kya hota hai?**

Every line in Dockerfile â†’ **Ek layer**

Advantage:
âœ” Cache use hota
âœ” Fast image builds
âœ” Efficient storage

---

### âœ… **Q12: Immutable Infrastructure?**

Image ban chuki â†’ change nahi hota
Change chahiye â†’ **new version image**

Production safe rahta âœ…

---

### âœ… **Q13: Container Networking kya hota hai?**

Containers **bridge network** ke through baat karte:

Example:
App â†’ MySQL
8080 â†’ 3306

---

### âœ… **One-Line Hero Answer (Jab Interviewer Detail Maange)**

> â€œImage is a packaged application,
> Container is that application running in isolation,
